 should provide the mechanistic class label.\n\nGiven the task asks to \"Classify the mechanistic class... and identify the reaction center\", I should provide both.\n\nThe mechanistic class is nucleophilic addition (enolate to carbocation). The reaction center is the formation of the C:10-C:20 bond."
